class="doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.291085100" property="sameAs">https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.291085100</a></div></div><div class="info-panel"><div class="info-panel__left-content"><div class="info-panel__metrics info-panel__item"></div></div><div class="info-panel__right-content"><div class="info-panel__article_tools info-panel__item">



        
